    {
      "start": 64.14,
      "end": 65.6,
      "text": "갓사이진."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.6,
      "end": 67.08,
      "text": "갓세균인데?"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.28,
      "end": 67.68,
      "text": "갓쓰근."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.76,
      "end": 68.56,
      "text": "Yeah, 갓쓰근."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.72,
      "end": 71.0,
      "text": "I heard an announcer say his name."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.26,
      "end": 71.66,
      "text": "갓쓰근."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.84,
      "end": 73.18,
      "text": "And he said 갓쓰근."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.24,
      "end": 73.48,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.74,
      "end": 75.14,
      "text": "So, 부드럽게 갓쓰근."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.2,
      "end": 76.58,
      "text": "기억이 계속 나야 될 텐데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.6,
      "end": 77.5,
      "text": "기억이 안 나면 잭."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.6,
      "end": 78.0,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.24,
      "end": 80.58,
      "text": "훨씬 더 좋은 방향을 알려주셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.68,
      "end": 81.44,
      "text": "잭 가요."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.58,
      "end": 83.24,
      "text": "And his character has the same name."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.32,
      "end": 84.74,
      "text": "Yeah, but a little bit different."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.94,
      "end": 85.38,
      "text": "잭."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.66,
      "end": 85.96,
      "text": "잭."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.96,
      "end": 86.52,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.58,
      "end": 87.2,
