    {
      "start": 88.38,
      "end": 88.64,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.88,
      "end": 90.38,
      "text": "C 철자가 빠지게 되는."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.56,
      "end": 90.92,
      "text": "아하."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.98,
      "end": 97.96,
      "text": "Yeah, 그래서 Z-A-K라는 철자를 새롭게 가지고 이 영화에서 배역을 맡았었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.98,
      "end": 99.3,
      "text": "Anyway, Zach이랑, Zach."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.4,
      "end": 99.52,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.72,
      "end": 100.44,
      "text": "잘 별로 없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.62,
      "end": 100.8,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.98,
      "end": 101.38,
      "text": "Zach."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.76,
      "end": 105.38,
      "text": "어쨌든, he's a main character in the movie, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.38,
      "end": 106.38,
      "text": "He is a star in the movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.46,
      "end": 108.66,
      "text": "And this was his breakout role."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.04,
      "end": 110.98,
      "text": "I had never heard of him before that."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.48,
      "end": 114.34,
      "text": "He was from, since he was a little kid,"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.34,
      "end": 116.54,
      "text": "his dream was to be an actor."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.18,
      "end": 119.9,
      "text": "So he acted in musicals and plays."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.72,
      "end": 122.46,
      "text": "He went to regular public school."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.56,
      "end": 122.96,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.1,
      "end": 125.46,
      "text": "Even though he's disabled, he has Down syndrome."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.08,
      "end": 128.18,
      "text": "His parents put him in a public school."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.28,
      "end": 128.6,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.64,
      "end": 130.64,
      "text": "And they just put him in with the other kids."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.86,
      "end": 131.16,
      "text": "Amazing."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.26,
      "end": 132.58,
      "text": "And he loved acting."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.68,
      "end": 133.56,
      "text": "He fell in love with acting."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.16,
      "end": 134.6,
      "text": "Wonderful."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.3,
      "end": 139.42,
      "text": "그리고, I heard he was the motivation or inspiration for this film."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.68,
      "end": 140.06,
      "text": "Is that right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.2,
      "end": 140.46,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.46,
      "end": 144.5,
      "text": "Actually, he went to a camp for disabled and non-disabled people."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.98,
      "end": 150.74,
      "text": "And he worked with counselors who work in acting and movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 151.06,
      "end": 153.48,
      "text": "And he said, I want to be a movie star."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.62,
      "end": 155.04,
      "text": "Make me a movie star."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.52,
      "end": 160.54,
      "text": "So the directors, they actually wrote this script about his life."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.66,
      "end": 161.02,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.02,
      "end": 166.04,
      "text": "They changed the story, of course, but it's based or inspired by Zach's life."
    },
    {
      "start": 166.2,
      "end": 167.26,
      "text": "What an inspiration."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.76,
      "end": 171.72,
      "text": "And they worked really hard to make him appear in this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.88,
      "end": 175.4,
      "text": "It was not easy to find funding and to make it happen."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.54,
      "end": 178.62,
      "text": "It took many, many years, but they put him on the big screen."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.72,
      "end": 181.0,
      "text": "And this was his breakout role."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.0,
      "end": 181.12,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.22,
      "end": 182.34,
      "text": "They made it, 그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.64,
      "end": 182.88,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.0,
      "end": 183.24,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.36,
      "end": 184.7,
      "text": "It was a very good idea."
    },
    {
      "start": 184.7,
      "end": 185.14,
      "text": "It was a very sweet idea."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.7,
      "end": 187.0,
      "text": "It sounds so sweet."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.22,
      "end": 187.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.66,
      "end": 191.0,
      "text": "It turned out amazing."
    },
    {
      "start": 191.02,
      "end": 192.0,
      "text": "Let's see this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.2,
      "end": 192.88,
      "text": "We got to see it."
    },
    {
      "start": 193.62,
      "end": 195.94,
      "text": "매일 시간 이렇게 강조하고 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 196.38,
      "end": 197.8,
      "text": "자, 오늘 내용 먼저 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.8,
      "end": 206.24,
      "text": "You let a half-naked boy with down syndrome who has no money, no family, and no idea how to get along in this world,"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.32,
      "end": 208.74,
      "text": "just slip out from under your nose in the thin air."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.26,
      "end": 213.06,
      "text": "And you have no idea where he is, where he's at, who he might be with?"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.2,
      "end": 213.88,
      "text": "Actually, I..."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.88,
      "end": 215.6,
      "text": "The nurses tell me you two are close."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.4,
      "end": 216.78,
      "text": "We are."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.78,
      "end": 220.72,
      "text": "Well, then you'll figure out where he's at, and you'll bring him back before I have"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.72,
      "end": 222.06,
      "text": "to report this to the state."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.06,
      "end": 227.89,
      "text": "네, 여태까지 잭가 tried to escape the facility twice."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.95,
      "end": 228.39,
      "text": "Two times."
    },
    {
      "start": 228.49,
      "end": 229.21,
      "text": "Yeah, so far."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.31,
      "end": 229.81,
      "text": "He failed."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.33,
      "end": 230.85,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.95,
      "end": 231.55,
      "text": "Failed twice."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.77,
      "end": 233.71,
      "text": "그런데, finally he made it."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.83,
      "end": 233.91,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 234.17,
      "end": 234.47,
      "text": "Freedom!"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.47,
      "end": 239.29,
      "text": "그런데 이게 어떻게 탈출을 했는지 장면들이 막 기억이 나는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.49,
      "end": 240.17,
      "text": "You remember that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.29,
      "end": 242.03,
      "text": "Yeah, with Carl's help."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.29,
      "end": 242.81,
      "text": "His roommate."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.97,
      "end": 243.17,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.45,
      "end": 248.83,
      "text": "His elderly roommate, he's like a grandfather, helped him escape through a barred window."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.95,
      "end": 249.35,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.85,
      "end": 253.01,
      "text": "그리고 또, he spread oil on his body."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.21,
      "end": 254.71,
      "text": "It was soap, I think."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.71,
      "end": 261.71,
      "text": "Yeah, anyway, there were bars on the window, so they like pulled the bars apart, and it"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.71,
      "end": 267.93,
      "text": "left a very thin space, narrow space, and he put soap all over his body, and he was wearing"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.93,
      "end": 271.83,
      "text": "only underwear, and he slipped through the window to freedom."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.33,
      "end": 275.81,
      "text": "와, 진짜 너무 흥미진진한 장면이었던 게 기억이 납니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.33,
      "end": 278.83,
      "text": "오이를 바른 게 아니고 비누였군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.99,
      "end": 280.23,
      "text": "아, 이제 좀 기억이 나는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.23,
      "end": 282.39,
      "text": "Anyway, oil, soap, something slippery."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.49,
      "end": 282.81,
      "text": "그죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.89,
      "end": 285.29,
      "text": "So you can squeeze through that narrow space."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.29,
      "end": 290.33,
      "text": "네, 그래서 결국 속옷만 입은 채 철창을 탈출하게 되는데, 이 철창을"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.33,
      "end": 292.53,
      "text": "구부리는 것 자체가 이렇게 쉬운 일은 아니잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.63,
      "end": 293.57,
      "text": "Who did that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.95,
      "end": 294.59,
      "text": "Was that Zach?"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.59,
      "end": 295.23,
      "text": "Zach himself."
    },
    {
      "start": 295.35,
      "end": 297.45,
      "text": "Yeah, he was very strong."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.55,
      "end": 298.19,
      "text": "Super strong."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.33,
      "end": 298.69,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.93,
      "end": 301.89,
      "text": "아주 powerful한 그런 힘을 가지고 있는 친구입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.49,
      "end": 304.51,
      "text": "네, 어떤 표현들이 있는지 먼저 알아볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.01,
      "end": 306.25,
      "text": "Half-naked boy."
    },
    {
      "start": 306.25,
      "end": 311.75,
      "text": "아, half-naked boy 라고 했으니까, 반 나체 소년이라는 건데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.77,
      "end": 315.41,
      "text": "Yeah, usually if you say half-naked boy, I think of a boy without a shirt."
    },
    {
      "start": 315.53,
      "end": 315.81,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.17,
      "end": 321.51,
      "text": "셔츠가 없는 상태를 나타낼 때도 이와 같이 half-naked라는 형용사로 표현을"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.51,
      "end": 327.89,
      "text": "하실 수가 있지만, 이 영화에서는 셔츠뿐 아니라 하의까지도, 특히"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.89,
      "end": 330.85,
      "text": "속옷만 빼고는 다 벗은 상태로 탈출을 하게 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.85,
      "end": 334.15,
      "text": "Yeah, I would say 80% naked, about 80%."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.15,
      "end": 334.61,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.81,
      "end": 336.31,
      "text": "Only in his underwear."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.33,
      "end": 336.89,
      "text": "90% 아니에요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.61,
      "end": 338.43,
      "text": "90%로 할까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.57,
      "end": 338.67,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.91,
      "end": 339.83,
      "text": "아무튼 briefs."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.83,
      "end": 340.33,
      "text": "알겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.33,
      "end": 341.69,
      "text": "Not boxers, but briefs."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.69,
      "end": 342.21,
      "text": "아, 야, 야."
    },
    {
      "start": 342.35,
      "end": 342.95,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 343.13,
      "end": 343.67,
      "text": "Like T-panty 같은."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.21,
      "end": 345.65,
      "text": "He's wearing just that."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.91,
      "end": 346.49,
      "text": "No way."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.97,
      "end": 347.41,
      "text": "No way."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.67,
      "end": 348.11,
      "text": "Yes way."
    },
    {
      "start": 348.37,
      "end": 348.85,
      "text": "아, 네."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.72,
      "end": 353.0,
      "text": "Slip out from under your nose into thin air."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.0,
      "end": 355.68,
      "text": "오, 이거 너무 재미있는 표현이었던 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.06,
      "end": 362.64,
